<h3 id="4tar">4.<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">tar</code></h3>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">tar</span> <span class="nt">-zpcv</span> <span class="nt">-f</span> /root/etc.tar.gz2 /etc
压缩 <span class="nb">tar</span> <span class="nt">-jcv</span> <span class="nt">-f</span> filename.tar.bz2 /要压缩的目录
查询 <span class="nb">tar</span> <span class="nt">-jtv</span> <span class="nt">-f</span> filename.tar.bz2
解压缩 <span class="nb">tar</span> <span class="nt">-jxv</span> <span class="nt">-f</span> filename.tar.bz2 <span class="nt">-C</span> /欲解压的目录
